long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Introduction
Papa's Wingeria is a mouthwatering time management and simulation game developed by Flipline Studios. In this exciting game, players get to run their own chicken wing restaurant, where they fry, sauce, and serve up a variety of delicious wings to satisfy hungry customers. With its addictive gameplay and tantalizing food options, Papa's Wingeria is sure to leave you craving for more!

Gameplay
In Papa's Wingeria, players take on the role of a new employee at Papa's chicken wing restaurant. The objective is to take customer orders, fry the wings to perfection, toss them in a variety of flavorful sauces, and serve them with the requested sides. The game offers a wide range of wing flavors, sauces, and sides, allowing players to create unique combinations for each customer. As you progress, you can unlock new ingredients, sauces, and decorations to enhance your menu.
